Comment: 0,0:00:20.26,0:00:25.31,translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}All by my lonesome, I was powerless, and so
Comment: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:30.81,translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}I really held no kind of value at all
Comment: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:36.01,translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}Faced with that emptiness and drowning in it
Comment: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:41.93,translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}I was always so anxious about tomorrow
Comment: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:47.30,translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}And by some random chance, the people I met back then
Comment: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:52.62,translation,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}Called me their friend without a second thought
